item.title: Senator Tim Kaine
item.description: Timothy Michael “Tim” Kaine (born February 26, 1958) is an American attorney and politician who is the junior United States Senator from Virginia. A Democrat, Kaine was elected to the Senate in 2012 and was the nominee of his party for Vice President of the United States in the 2016 election.
